# Environment Variables for $WISH Token Integration

# ==============================================
# TOKEN CONTRACT (Add when deployed on Pump.fun)
# ==============================================
# NEXT_PUBLIC_WISH_TOKEN_CONTRACT=your_solana_contract_address_here

# ==============================================
# SOCIAL MEDIA (Add when created)
# ==============================================
# NEXT_PUBLIC_WISH_TOKEN_TWITTER=https://twitter.com/your_token_handle

# ==============================================
# API KEYS FOR HOLDER DATA
# Choose either Helius OR Moralis (or both for redundancy)
# ==============================================

# Option 1: Helius API (Recommended for Solana)
# Get your API key at: https://dev.helius.xyz/
# HELIUS_API_KEY=your_helius_api_key_here

# Option 2: Moralis API
# Get your API key at: https://moralis.io/
# MORALIS_API_KEY=your_moralis_api_key_here

# ==============================================
# INSTRUCTIONS FOR WHEN YOU'RE READY TO LAUNCH:
# ==============================================
# 
# 1. Deploy $WISH token on Pump.fun
# 2. Copy the contract address
# 3. Uncomment NEXT_PUBLIC_WISH_TOKEN_CONTRACT and paste address
# 4. Create Twitter account for $WISH
# 5. Uncomment NEXT_PUBLIC_WISH_TOKEN_TWITTER and add URL
# 6. Sign up for Helius (free tier available)
# 7. Uncomment HELIUS_API_KEY and paste your key
# 8. In app/api/token/holders/route.ts, uncomment the Helius code block
# 9. Restart your dev server (npm run dev)
# 10. Visit /wishtoken to see live data!
#
# The page is fully ready - just plug in these values when available.
